        " مَنْ أَكَلَ سَبْعَ تَمَرَاتٍ عَجْوَةٍ عِنْدَ مَنَامِهِ قَتَلْنَ الدِّيدَانَ مِنْ بَطْنِهِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "From him, from Yaqoub Bin Yazeed, from Ziyad Bin Marwan Al Qindy, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The one who eats seven <span class=\"iTxt\">Ajwa</span> dates at his sleep time, would kill the insects in his belly’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "20. It is narrated from the narrator of the previous Hadith from Ya’qub ibn from Ziyad ibn Marwan al-Qandiy from ‘Abd Allah ibn Sinan who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Eating seven dates of al-‘Ajwah at bed time kill the worms in one’s belly.”’ "
        ]
      }
